+# PyStudio Termux Source Termux
+
+Shared primary Termux package source adapter for PyStudio. This repository is
+the PyStudio fork of the upstream Termux package tree.
+
+This repository owns package source files, build scripts, and source-side
+patches only. Toolchain builds are triggered from thin child repositories and
+orchestrated by `vg188/pystudio-termux-builds`.
+
+## Upstream Maintenance
+
+Upstream remote:
+
+```sh
+git remote add upstream https://github.com/termux/termux-packages.git
+git remote set-url --push upstream DISABLED
+```
+
+Recommended update flow:
+
+```sh
+git fetch upstream
+git checkout master
+git merge upstream/master
+```
+
+After resolving conflicts, run focused builds through the thin child
+repositories before publishing broad runtime package updates. Keep PyStudio
+package-name, Android-prefix, download hardening, and dependency-trim patches
+in this source adapter, not in the thin toolchain repositories.
